			<div class="question">Question 3: Describe the selection procedure of that company.</div>

				<div class="answer">Answer:  For Mentor Graphics, there was an initial shortlisting based on resume. And then one single Technical Interview Round. 
				For NXP Semiconductors, there were three rounds during the recruitment process. There was an initial shortlisting as well based on CGPA. First round was an Online Test comprising 20 MCQs, 4 subjective questions and 3 design questions. Second round was Technical Interview round. The last round was the HR Interview.
